{"3787390": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Love or Lust Beach Stories", "steam_appid": 3787390, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h1>❤️‍🔥ADD TO WISHLIST❤️‍🔥</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3787390/extras/673aeb7a4d79ae44ff533dcf929450d1.avif?t=1771602648\" width=780 height=220 /></span></p></p><br><h1>關於此遊戲</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3787390/extras/2b18ee249e690394c4f542ed5f8a585b.avif?t=1771602648\" width=780 height=536 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3787390/extras/93be684d1b966f486b7362d5010eac3a.avif?t=1771602648\" width=780 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>歡迎來到愛或慾望：海灘物語——一場陽光灑落、熱帶海灘上的成人故事冒險。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一名尋找暑期工作的大学生，或許也想要一點曖昧。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >當你進入一家時尚的海灘酒吧打工時，局勢瞬間升溫。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3787390/extras/4bca904df6875ce254ec733775c16e83.poster.avif?t=1771602648\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3787390/extras/4bca904df6875ce254ec733775c16e83.webm?t=1771602648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3787390/extras/4bca904df6875ce254ec733775c16e83.mp4?t=1771602648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >俊美陌生人、神祕儀式、古老傳說，以及意義重大的選擇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，當夕陽變得愈發詭異，雞尾酒開始低聲吐露祕密…… </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你意識到，這個夏天或許不只會改變你的人生，還可能改變整個世界。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3787390/extras/cd2a0fd80e7719f3cc79d7978e503e5c.poster.avif?t=1771602648\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3787390/extras/cd2a0fd80e7719f3cc79d7978e503e5c.webm?t=1771602648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3787390/extras/cd2a0fd80e7719f3cc79d7978e503e5c.mp4?t=1771602648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🍸誘惑滿點、劇情濃厚的體驗</strong><br>沉浸於分支式成人敘事，你的選擇將帶來不同結局、火熱場景或心碎瞬間。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🍸暗藏祕密的酒吧</strong><br>發現古老遺物、失落儀式，以及埋藏在沙下的隱秘衝突。愛真的能拯救世界嗎？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🍸調酒攻心</strong><br>精通調酒配方與小遊戲，魅惑客人，解鎖隱藏故事，並搖動局勢。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🍸洞察模式</strong><br>使用收集的「能量」啟動特殊對話選項，揭露潛藏慾望或秘密路徑。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🍸光明 vs. 慾望</strong><br>你會不惜一切追求快感，還是犧牲自己守護所愛？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🍸私訊加溫</strong><br>透過訊息、自拍與情感告白，甚至大膽裸照，建立關係。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3787390/extras/c367b70a42902ec23981eb04de524b23.poster.avif?t=1771602648\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3787390/extras/c367b70a42902ec23981eb04de524b23.webm?t=1771602648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3787390/extras/c367b70a42902ec23981eb04de524b23.mp4?t=1771602648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>適合喜愛《夏日狂想曲：鄉間的難忘回憶》、《Leisure Suit Larry》、《College Kings》以及帶有獨特轉折的